  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "What is a Favicon?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "A favicon is a small icon displayed in the browser tab, bookmarks, and address bar that represents your website."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Basic Syntax"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" href=\"favicon.png\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Where to Add Favicon?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "The favicon link should be placed inside the <head> section of your HTML document."
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<head>\n  <link rel=\"icon\" href=\"favicon.ico\">\n</head>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Supported Formats"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "value": {
        "headers": ["Format", "Description"],
        "rows": [
          ["ICO", "Most widely supported"],
          ["PNG", "Modern and high-quality"],
          ["SVG", "Scalable vector format"],
          ["GIF", "Supports animation (limited use)"]
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Multiple Icon Sizes"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"32x32\" href=\"favicon-32.png\">\n<link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"16x16\" href=\"favicon-16.png\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Apple Touch Icon"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"apple-icon.png\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Best Practices"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Use .ico or PNG for compatibility**",
        "**Provide multiple sizes for different devices**",
        "**Keep favicon simple and recognizable**",
        "**Optimize file size for performance**",
        "**Place favicon in root directory for fallback**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Common Mistakes"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Incorrect file path**",
        "**Using unsupported formats**",
        "**Not adding favicon in head section**",
        "**Large file size affecting performance**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Conclusion"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "A favicon enhances branding and user experience by making your website easily identifiable in browser tabs and bookmarks."
    }
